File:Nagahatabe-jinja(Kamisato-machi,Nagahama) Honden.jpg|Honden
File:Nagahatabe-jinja(Kamisato-machi,Nagahama) Inari-jinja.jpg|Inari shrine
</gallery>

=== Events ===
* Spring festival (March 19)<ref name="Nagahatabe Shrine origin" />
* Autumn festival (October 19)<ref name="Nagahatabe Shrine origin" />

=== Access ===
* From JR {{ill|lt=Takasaki Line|Q1346657|qid=Q1346657|1=Takasaki Line}}{{ill|lt=Jinbohara Station|Q845133|qid=Q845133|1=Jimbohara Station}}, take Kamisato town bus Komugicchi-go (south route) bound for "Unicus" from "Nishihara-chō" stop; get off at final stop "Minami Gomyō Kōkaidō," then 15 min walk.
* From JR {{ill|lt=Takasaki Line|Q1346657|qid=Q1346657|1=Takasaki Line}}{{ill|lt=Honjō Station|Q844906|qid=Q844906|1=Honjō Station (Saitama)}}, take Asahi Bus bound for "Kansen Sōgō Shisho"; get off at "Sanchō," 30 min walk.
* From JR {{ill|lt=Hachikō Line|Q1372071|qid=Q1372071|1=Hachikō Line}}{{ill|lt=Tanshō Station|Q845044|qid=Q845044|1=Tanshō Station}}, take Asahi Bus bound for "Honjō Station South Exit"; get off at "Sanchō," 30 min walk.

